text: Anguilla national football team is the national football team of Anguilla. Anguilla is currently 198th out of 203 in the FIFA World Rankings. ==World Cup record== * 1930 to 1990 – Did not exist * 1994 to 1998 – Did not enter * 2002 to 2014 – Did not qualify ==References== Category:Football in British Overseas Territories Category:Anguilla Category:Caribbean national football teams
